reviewText: The DVD I received was a mess and had to be returned, which was too bad because the little I saw of it was really good information. So even though I didn't get to see most of it I want to encourage others to go ahead and get it, hence 4 stars.

I bought this originally from the Stan Winston School site but wanted to share my review here too.  This course is AMAZING!  My project came out so much better because of this.  Thank you Stan Winston School!
